ntary"><ref target="1910-09-18" type="schnitzlerDiary" subtype="see"/></note>, vorher <rs ref="#pmb882" type="place">Heidelberg</rs>.</p><closer>Herzlichste Grüsse Ihnen Allen! <signed>O. S.</signed></closer></div></body><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb2121">
